{"parentUuid":"67befb5a-1cdc-47e5-9cc2-f1e1d926b3ba","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"1c862c16-8e40-4888-9958-d76a6e20c83e","agentId":"a918bea6edbdf1409","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AbpMMGgLTq35JtnWGyAwtv","type":"tool_result","content":"    90→### 能力 2：时间窗口切片\n    91→\n    92→**输入：** `--time \"14:23:05\"`（格式宽松，支持 `HH:MM:SS` / `YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS` / `HH:MM`）\n    93→**行为：**\n    94→1. 解析目标时间点\n    95→2. 找到日志中时间戳最接近该时间点的行\n    96→3. 提取该行前后 ±30 秒内的所有日志行\n    97→4. 若日志无时间戳：取目标行（或文件起始行）上下各 25 行\n    98→\n    99→**输出：** 时间切片内的所有日志行，`ERROR`/`FATAL`/`Fault` 级别行用 `⚠️` 标记\n   100→\n   101→### 能力 3：符号提取\n   102→\n   103→**从以下位置提取业务代码符号：**\n   104→- iOS Crash Log 崩溃帧（业务 Bundle 帧）\n   105→- `Exception Reason:` / `Termination Reason:` 行\n   106→- 自定义日志中的类名/方法名模式\n   107→\n   108→**提取规则：**\n   109→- OC 类名（业务代码首选）：`XP[A-Z][A-Za-z]+`（小鹏业务前缀正则，精确匹配业务类）→ **权重：高**\n   110→- OC 类名（通用降权提取）：`[A-Z][A-Za-z]+`（系统/第三方类权重低）→ **权重：低**\n   111→- OC 方法：`-\\[[A-Za-z]+ [a-zA-Z:]+\\]` 或 `+\\[[A-Za-z]+ [a-zA-Z:]+\\]`\n   112→- Swift 符号：`<Module>.<ClassName>.<methodName>` 格式\n   113→- 关键词命中：若用户传入 `--keyword`，优先提取包含该关键词的符号\n   114→\n   115→**过滤规则（降低权重，非排除）：**\n   116→- 系统框架：`com.apple.*`、`libsystem_*`、`libdispatch`、`UIKitCore`、`CoreFoundation`\n   117→- 过滤后若无业务符号：标注「未找到业务符号，建议先符号化日志」，保留原始帧\n   118→\n   119→### 能力 4：错误类型归类\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"uuid":"d2804878-3878-4d2c-bca8-138703271fd4","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:38:04.068Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"67befb5a-1cdc-47e5-9cc2-f1e1d926b3ba","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/xpeng/Desktop/AiStudy/claude-learn/plugin-dev","sessionId":"95b3d4f4-8123-4885-9752-f1e600f4a1f6","version":"2.1